  <header>
    <h1>Register your church, business or organization with City English Project (CEP)!</h1>
    <hr>
    <h4>
      When you [successfully] click the button, "Send this form to CEP" below, we will send an email to you.  In that email, we will then direct you to our "CEP Volunteer Application Form." After you fill it out and submit it, will respond to you within 48 hours. 
